      "width": 560,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Examples\n\n**Valid:**\n- host.navigate_port -> target.root\n- host.consume_view -> target.port_view\n\n**Invalid (must fail):**\n- bridge authority inferred from a rendered card\n- runtime behavior granted because a target view happens to exist\n- incompatible semantic types connected without an explicit wildcard policy",
